Would it be possible to address [this comment](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/34435#discussion_r3116469297) in this PR as well? Something like the following should work:
```diff
--- a/src/node/blockstorage.h
+++ b/src/node/blockstorage.h
@@ -18,6 +18,8 @@
 #include <streams.h>
 #include <sync.h>
 #include <uint256.h>
+// IWYU incorrectly suggests removing this header.
+// See https://github.com/include-what-you-use/include-what-you-use/issues/2014.
 #include <util/byte_units.h> // IWYU pragma: keep
 #include <util/expected.h>
 #include <util/fs.h>
```
